videos.description: Allonzo Trier takes the ball in the paint and cuts through the Northern Arizona defense with the layup.
videos.headline: Trier drives to the rack to extend Arizona's lead

videos.description: Dusan Ristic sets a pick-and-roll to the basket for an easy dunk assisted by Parker Jackson-Cartwright.
videos.headline: Arizona ball movement leads to easy bucket

videos.description: After grabbing the rebound on the defensive end, Emmanuel Akot goes up the floor and makes the layup despite the contact.
videos.headline: Arizona's Akot converts layup

videos.description: Emmanuel Akot fires a pass to Allonzo Trier in transition for a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Trier skies for one-handed slam

videos.description: Arizona's Alex Barcello finds Parker Jackson-Cartwright in the corner for the open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Barcello finds Jackson-Cartwright for the corner 3

videos.description: Arizona's Deandre Ayton rejects Torry Johnson's layup attempt into the crowd.
videos.headline: Ayton sends block into stands

videos.description: Allonzo Trier takes the pass in transition and throws down the one-handed slam in the second half.
videos.headline: Trier throws down dunk in transition

videos.description: Alex Barcello finds Dusan Ristic off the pick-and-roll for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Barcello finds Ristic off pick-and-roll

videos.description: DeAndre Ayton grabs the missed shot and emphatically throws down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Ayton throws down dunk after rebound

videos.description: DeAndre Ayton throws a one-handed bounce pass to Allonzo Trier in transition for the finger roll layup.
videos.headline: Ayton sets up Trier transition layup

videos.description: Tyler Trillo scores his first points as a Wildcat on the corner 3-pointer assisted by Jake DesJardins.
videos.headline: Trillo scores first career points on the corner 3
